                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-95-defend706 t18010701-95-punish512"></join>
               within one month to stand in the pillory at the west end of Cheapside for one hour between the hours of twelve and two
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
